==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Regain
<hw>Re*gain"</hw> <pr>(r?*g?n")</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>re-</ets> + <ets>gain</ets>: cf. F. <ets>regagner</ets>.]</ety>
<def>To gain anew; to get again; to recover, as what has escaped or been
lost; to reach again.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- To recover; reobtain; repossess;
retrieve.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Regal</ent>⟦br⟧
